---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Projects"
  description="Current projects: Kink Archetypes personality assessment, Jules AI framework, educational content, and more."
>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Projects</h1>

    <div class="project-card">
      <h3><a href="https://quiz.9archetypes.app">Kink Archetypes</a></h3>
      <span class="status">Live</span>
      <p>
        Interactive personality assessment exploring kink education for adult audiences. Identifies relationship and communication styles across 9 archetypes.
        React + TypeScript frontend, PHP + MySQL backend. 200+ daily users.
      </p>
      <p><a href="https://quiz.9archetypes.app">quiz.9archetypes.app &rarr;</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="project-card">
      <h3><a href="/jules/">Jules</a></h3>
      <span class="status">Active</span>
      <p>
        Open-source AI assistant framework built on Claude Code. Custom personality, decision framework, autonomous workflows, VPS infrastructure.
        33 skills, 15 rules, 12 hooks.
      </p>
      <p><a href="https://github.com/jonathanmalkin/jules">GitHub &rarr;</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="project-card">
      <h3>Articles &amp; Content</h3>
      <span class="status">Active</span>
      <p>
        Educational articles and a subscriber newsletter covering Claude Code, AI agents, and solo founding. Published at builtwithjon.com.
        Built with Astro v6, hosted on Cloudflare.
      </p>
      <p><a href="/articles/">Read the articles &rarr;</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="project-card">
      <h3>What's Next</h3>
      <span class="status">In Development</span>
      <p>
        Expanding the assessment toolkit in two directions: more tools for the kink education space
        (interest exploration, negotiation frameworks) and personal development assessments for
        general audiences. Same interactive assessment approach, new domains.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
